attributes.Long form description: The student prepares the shelves with which he is going to assemble his furniture. He prepares the legs and starts to assemble the table. He lays the furniture down, grabs the hex socket head, and screws it but it costs him a bit of work, and he takes another leg and aligns it, inserts the hex socket heads and secures them with an allen wrench, turns the furniture over, and places the last leg. He turns the furniture over and places the second shelf, inserts the hex socket heads, and turns them with the allen wrench, stops the furniture, lays it down again, and checks the hex socket heads by using the allen wrench. Finally, he just secures the hex socket heads.
